Research Data Consultations

Introduction

Research data consultations are booked in 1 hour blocks. Students are encouraged to returen throughout project development, including during planning, collection, cleaning and analyis, and presentation. To help maintain a focus on learning, students deposit data on UBC’s OneDrive, where consultants, when possible, help with demonstration code on only a subset of the deposited data.

UBCO Biology funding started September, 2024, with 1 TA position in W1 and 2 TA positions in W2.
